<item>
            <title>[DERBY-5708] simpleThread test doesn&apos;t release connection</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-5708</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The simpleThread test, which is run by LangHarnessJavaTest, stores its connection in a static field. It doesn&apos;t close the connection, or clear the static field, before returning. So the connection is left open for the rest of the test run (potentially for the entire duration of suites.All).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
